### 获取所有航班
GET http://localhost:5130/api/flights

### 获取特定航班
GET http://localhost:5130/api/flights/1

### 根据条件搜索航班
GET http://localhost:5130/api/flights?origin=北京&destination=上海

### 创建新航班
POST http://localhost:5130/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flightNumber": "CX1001",
  "origin": "香港",
  "destination": "北京",
  "departureTime": "2025-01-15T10:00:00",
  "arrivalTime": "2025-01-15T13:30:00",
  "price": 1200.00,
  "availableSeats": 200,
  "totalSeats": 250,
  "aircraft": "Boeing 777-300"
}

### 检查航班可用性
GET http://localhost:5130/api/flights/1/availability?passengers=2

### 获取活跃订阅
GET http://localhost:5130/api/subscriptions/active

### 获取客户订阅
GET http://localhost:5130/api/subscriptions/customer/1

### 创建新订阅
POST http://localhost:5130/api/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "origin": "深圳",
  "destination": "上海",
  "maxPrice": 800.00,
  "emailNotifications": true,
  "smsNotifications": false
}

### 订单：创建
POST http://localhost:5130/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingNumber": "BK20250910-001",
  "passengerName": "张三",
  "flightNumber": "MU5123",
  "departureTime": "2025-09-20T09:30:00Z",
  "quantity": 2,
  "unitPrice": 899.00
}

### 订单：按 Id 获取（替换 {id}）
GET http://localhost:5130/api/orders/{id}

### 订单：确认（替换 {id}）
POST http://localhost:5130/api/orders/{id}/confirm

### 订单：取消（替换 {id}）
POST http://localhost:5130/api/orders/{id}/cancel
